{
  "id": "adv_card_smr_12_03",
  "title": "奥山すみれ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ゲーム発売後",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 1.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "おはようございます！　……えいっ！\nエールちゅーちゅーミラクルぽん！",
      "startTime": 5.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（また出合い頭に魔法がきたぞ……！？）\n（この間のことを考えると……こうだ！）",
      "startTime": 11.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "すみれのおかげで仕事の疲れが\n全部吹き飛んだ気がするぞー？",
      "startTime": 18.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "違いますよ、もう！　今のは時が止まる魔法です！\nこの前のとは詠唱も違うじゃないですか！",
      "startTime": 26.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "時が……！？　す、すまんすまん\nそれじゃ……か、かちーん……",
      "startTime": 32.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "わーい！　魔法が成功しました！\nこの間に{user}さんにイタズラを……！",
      "startTime": 41.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……すみれ。喜んでいるところ悪いが、\nまだ魔法を習得しようとしていたのか？",
      "startTime": 48.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、あの時は心配させちゃってすみません\nもう大丈夫ですよ！",
      "startTime": 56.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "それなら良かったよ。それにしても、すっかり魔法\n少女の役をものにしたな。演技も好評だったぞ",
      "startTime": 62.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "嬉しいです！　リリースされるまで不安でしたけど\nSNSでもみんな喜んでくれていて凄く安心しました！",
      "startTime": 70.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "私の自然体の魔法少女が見られて良かった\nという意見が多くて、頑張ったかいがありました",
      "startTime": 79.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "他には、私が可愛過ぎて何度もプレイした、という\n意見もありましたね。え、えへへ……",
      "startTime": 89,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "……お兄ちゃんがヒントを掴むきっかけをくれた\nおかげです。ありがとうございます！",
      "startTime": 95.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ゲームが成功したのはすみれ達の頑張りの成果だよ\nお礼なら今度のPRイベントでファンに伝えるといい",
      "startTime": 103.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "今度のPRイベントではミニライブもあるから\n他のメンバーと一緒に沢山盛り上げてくれ",
      "startTime": 110.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんです！　ゲームの成功を祝って\nみんなでミニライブをすっごく盛り上げちゃいますよ！",
      "startTime": 116.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――PRイベント当日",
      "startTime": 121.633331867,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 123.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 123.1666641235
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "つ、ついに本番です\nちゃんとゲームの面白さとか伝えられるかな……",
      "startTime": 127.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "緊張しているみたいだけど、すみれなら大丈夫だ\n歌もMCも沢山練習してきたんだからな",
      "startTime": 136.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 139.6666631658
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんですけど、みんなの前で披露するのは\n初めてなので、落ち着かなくて……",
      "startTime": 143.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "そうか。……そういえば、俺も魔法を使えるんだ\nいくぞ……大丈夫だシャイニー！",
      "startTime": 152.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 154
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "……え、えーっと……{user}さん……？\n魔法は出ないのが普通ですよ……",
      "startTime": 160.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 163.2666631658
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "すみれが緊張しなくなるようにと思ったんだが……\n慣れないことはするものじゃなかったか……",
      "startTime": 167.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "……ふふっ。確かに、もう緊張しなくなりました\n{user}さんは魔法使いだったんですね",
      "startTime": 175.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 178.6999964992
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます。お兄ちゃんの魔法のおかげで\nミニライブでも緊張せずに話せそうです！",
      "startTime": 182.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 185.5999964992
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "しっかりと最後まで見守っているからな\n頑張れ、魔法少女ヴィオレット！",
      "startTime": 188.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 192.0999964992
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-smr015.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　行ってきます！\n魔法の力で、みんなをハッピーにしますよ！",
      "startTime": 194.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-smr016.m4a",
      "text": "今日はPRイベントに集まってくれて\nありがとうございます！",
      "startTime": 203.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-smr017.m4a",
      "text": "『サキュ×まほ』で魔法少女を\n演じました、奥山すみれです！",
      "startTime": 207.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-smr018.m4a",
      "text": "実は……今回、役作りに凄く悩んだんです\n自分らしい魔法少女ってなんだろう？　って……",
      "startTime": 215.6999908447,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-smr019.m4a",
      "text": "私は魔法が使える訳でも空が飛べる訳でもないから\n魔法少女の気持ちなんて分からなくて……",
      "startTime": 225.2666575114,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-smr020.m4a",
      "text": "でも……ある人が、私に空を飛べる魔法をかけてくれて\n私を魔法少女にしてくれたんです！",
      "startTime": 235.4999908447,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-smr021.m4a",
      "text": "だから、私はゲームの中の『魔法少女ヴィオレット』も\n本当の私だと思ってます！",
      "startTime": 244.23331604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-smr022.m4a",
      "text": "特に……大切な人のために、究極魔法を使うか\n使わないかの選択を迫られた時は……",
      "startTime": 251.2333282471,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
